{"id":595579,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/【立此存照】老大哥正在看你的推文？！请多发/","date":"2018-09-13T08:34:21Z","modified":"2018-09-13T08:34:21Z","title":"【立此存照】老大哥正在看你的推文？！请多发“正面”推","content":"<p>9月13日，中文推特圈流传一张图片，图片显示某办公场所内（有可能位于江苏淮安），正以大屏方式呈现“境外采集数据”。从内容上看，是以“淮安”为关键词显示twitter内容的搜索结果，并且系统还可以就内容进行“正面”、“中立”、“负面”的评级。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/DjeTO5FUYAAFgvH.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-595584\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/DjeTO5FUYAAFgvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/DjeTO5FUYAAFgvH.jpg 1920w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/DjeTO5FUYAAFgvH-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/DjeTO5FUYAAFgvH-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/DjeTO5FUYAAFgvH-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>虽然这个系统评级尚不准确，例如同样内容如果以繁体呈现，就会被认为“中立”；而对华春莹的辱骂则被认为是“正面”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/繁体.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-595585\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/繁体.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"94\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/繁体.jpg 706w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/繁体-300x51.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/华春莹.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-595586\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/华春莹.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"79\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/华春莹.jpg 615w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/华春莹-300x43.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这张图片令一些推友感到忧虑和不安，意识到twitter正被有关部门全方面地监控。然而另一些推友则认为，这个事情“不稀奇”，中国政府显然有监视twitter的强烈愿望，况且twitter内容本来就是以论坛形式公开化的，只需注意保护隐私即可。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%BA%91%E6%9E%81%E6%9D%83\">云极权</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%EF%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A8%81%E6%9D%83%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%A0%E5%AD%94/\">纽约时报｜中国的威权主义未来：人工智能与无孔不入的监控</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%E5%A5%87%E9%97%BB%E5%BD%95-%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E4%BA%91%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E5%85%9A%E8%AF%BE%E9%9A%8F%E8%BA%AB%E5%90%AC/\">【立此存照】 “红色云”助你党课随身听</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%A4%BEcna-%E8%90%A7%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80-%E6%9B%B4%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%8E%8C%E6%8E%A7%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A/\">中央社CNA | 萧强：中共运用科技 更全面掌控社会</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E6%9E%81%E6%9D%83%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D/\">【立此存照】在数字极权下的上海生活是怎样一种体验？</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%E5%93%81%E8%91%B1-%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E6%83%85%E6%8A%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%91%B3%E7%9D%80%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%EF%BC%9F/\">品葱 | 专栏文章：大情报意味着什么？</a></p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[8339,33700,33699,33619,26554,33617,9249,36099,13826,12251,10942,13684,13638,9212]}